{"tid":1598160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港全民議政會」(HK Assembly) Pre-Inaugural首投預備投票（臨立會法案）","createTime":"2019-09-27T09:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:26:41.000Z","uid":300718,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2afe42e3983335aa88ee27c9a1b6de0cb168a399","tid":1598160,"uid":300718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">投票Link： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=db3a348b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">是次投票內容</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">你希望「全民議政會」首先就以下哪一法案進行再投票？<br />\n1. 國旗及國徽條例<br />\n2. 公安條例<br />\n3. 社團條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">會徽初選 （上輪投票）</span></span><br />\n「香港全民議政會」會徽初選投票已於26/9晚完結。有賴眾議政公民支持，投票率高達93%，並由設計2及設計5得票最高。團隊的設計精英將會就獲選設計加以改良，然後再由大家再次投票，定出「香港全民議政會」的最終會徽！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">本次投票</span></span><br />\n首投議題將會是：對特區臨時立法會，所通過法案的再投票🏛<br />\n<br />\n臨時立法會(臨會) 作為首屆特區立法機關，只運作了一年五個月零五日（25/01/1997 - 30/06/1998），期間三讀通過六十多條法案，而當中不少法案對香港現況帶來相當大的爭議。但臨會並非由選舉產生的議員所組成，其決策相對更未必為大部份香港人所認同。因此，我們希望就當時所通過的法案進行再投票。<br />\n<br />\n在此之前，我們現投票選出第一條被討論及再投票的法案。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">規則</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 一人一票 [1]<br />\n2. 投票時間：27/9 6 PM - 29/9 6 PM （香港時間）<br />\n3. 以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=db3a348b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [2]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投票需要你</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 入Channel： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=db3a348b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. 投票<br />\n3. 叫朋友加入Channel一起投！</span><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題；2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高；3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n[2] 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"1cff76956e1ecded3fee14d02376d5afbd84c77d","tid":1598160,"uid":86828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"任巴會唔會解釋下呢幾條係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d624b0578cf5bb57ce43cdf3497b099d467e339","tid":1598160,"uid":33292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"741d21008de0e6b1ba949b0203633dfcc62a857e","tid":1598160,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n對抗假新聞假資訊，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【facebook戰線】大家一齊report曬D垃圾page，等佢地重蹈點新聞嘅覆轍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596798</a>"},{"pid":"90b4ef6e4ad45259d9ec3c265380c9dc95573f32","tid":1598160,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"投咗"},{"pid":"c95303fb23b852e618eb012de84636fb4b1cad76","tid":1598160,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立即普選 否則攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"40ea846f4d984f49b7e66ef